name: Eyes of Wisdom
description:
Eyes of Wisdom

Collection: Oh, Those Eyes!

Wisdom’s Eyes is the 2nd in a collection of animal eyes. More to come. Some of the images are based upon my original art and at least one is a photography. This is a work based upon one of my paintings in Ozark pigments. I’ve embellished it with digital touches to make this NFT.

I’m @wildozark on Twitter if you’d like to get in touch.

These images will also be available in limited edition real prints. More information about them can be found at wildozark.com/animal-eyes.
